  "detailed_description": "<h1>Season  : Esper</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/b0c099e8cbcefd69129ef21418499627.poster.avif?t=1736924584\" width=768 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/b0c099e8cbcefd69129ef21418499627.webm?t=1736924584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/b0c099e8cbcefd69129ef21418499627.mp4?t=1736924584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Alien  fight against the Red lord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Key Features: </strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/234bae3a59380234e4cab6a869fd9674.poster.avif?t=1736924584\" width=639 height=369 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/234bae3a59380234e4cab6a869fd9674.webm?t=1736924584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>    Hauntingly beautiful vistas and locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Freedom and Liberty  -Do whatever you want in a massive open world with hundreds of locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exotic Weapons  – Players will obtain a variety of weapon types.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Explore-  Explore Galaxy City .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     Galaxy City Map- Simple Galaxy City Map for easy progress and exploration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Teleportation Tower - Simple Teleportation Tower for Progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/2773d3a3f52d2651fb1911ec45fb06d8.poster.avif?t=1736924584\" width=676 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1800650/extras/2773d3a3f52d2651fb1911ec45fb06d8.webm?t=1736924584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        Great Soundtrack- Game has incredible orchestral  and Electronic music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Setting</strong></u> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy is suffering from Dark age,where life is cheap,there is no economy and culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy City  - Galaxy City is the capital of Trantord And Galaxy</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trantord - Trantord is planet where green people lives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terminus- Red lord has lost war at planet terminus..</p>",
